Package: MsBackendHmdb
Title: Mass spectrometry data backends for The Human Metabolome Database
Version: 0.2.0
Description: Mass spectrometry (MS) data backend supporting import and handling
	     of MS/MS spectra from the Human Metabolom Database (HMDB).
